entries.abort: Coward! I knew you didn't have it in you.
entries.arrived_at_loc: Maintain current position and wait for the arrival of the slave shuttle.
entries.attack_notify: FF0000 Tactical Computer: pcontrast1 < Enemy fighters detected. > pcontrast1
entries.attack_stopped: FF0000 Tactical Computer: pcontrast1 < Enemy fighters eliminated. > pcontrast1
entries.complete: Excellently done. I would like to have a word with you. Come back and see me.
entries.failed_destroy: Destroyed! Perhaps I misjudged your abilities.
entries.failed_protect: You left the slave shuttles wing! Your job is to protect the vessel and that is what I expected you to do.
entries.found_loc: The slave shuttle's arrival location has been sent to your navigation computer.
entries.goodbye_1: I am safely in Avatar space. Thanks, pilot.
entries.goodbye_3: I will be safe from here on in.
entries.goodbye_4: You better report back to Boshaz.
entries.goodbye_5: The Avatar has contacted me. I will be safe from here on in.
entries.hull_half: Hull at half strength. Get these fighters off of us!
entries.panic_2: Looks like we have some unwanted company.
entries.panic_3: Time to prove your worth to Zssik.
entries.panic_4: Ha! They sent out walking carpets to greet us.
entries.panic_5: Show them what you are made of.
entries.quest_escort_d: Follow and protect the slave shuttle until it can arrive in the Avatar's zone of control.
entries.quest_location_d: The slave shuttle will meet you in orbit around Kashyyyk.
entries.quest_rendezvous_d: Travel to the meeting location and wait for the arrival of the slave shuttle.
entries.reason_1: Ok, it is time to get moving.
entries.reason_2: I am going to take flight path Alpha to get to the Avatar.
entries.reason_3: My cargo isn't going to tame itself. Lets get moving.
entries.reason_4: I want to make this fast. My cargo is getting mad.
entries.shields_depleted: Shields down! We cannot last much longer.
entries.taunt_3: I will show you no mercy.
entries.taunt_4: The Wookiee people will never give up.
entries.thanks_1: Wow. You really taught those Wookiees a lesson.
entries.thanks_2: They are not so tough now.
entries.thanks_3: That is one way to tame a Wookiee.
entries.thanks_4: Impressive. You fly like a Trandoshan.
entries.thanks_5: Those poor little Wookiees never knew what hit them.
entries.title: Kashyyyk System: Escort the Zssik Slave Shuttle
entries.title_d: Boshaz has hired you to protect a slave shuttle traveling between Kashyyyk and the Avatar Space Platform.
